    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "When the bin width becomes large enough, `rose` diagram gives unexpected placements\r\n\r\n```\r\necho \"0.33 -90\" | gmt rose -JX10c -Bg -R0/1/0/360 -L -F -A10 -D -Gblue -png works\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\necho \"0.33 -90\" | gmt rose -JX10c -Bg -R0/1/0/360 -L -F -A20 -D -Gblue -png doesntwork\r\n```\r\n\r\nBest,\r\nGuillaume",
